earch for the maximum length of \"Pacific Bluefin Tuna\" on the Monterey Bay Aquarium website.\n\nAfter researching, we find that the Monterey Bay Aquarium states that the maximum length of a Pacific Bluefin Tuna can reach up to 3 meters.\n\nThe verified information confirms that the maximum length of the Pacific Bluefin Tuna according to the Monterey Bay Aquarium is **3 meters**.\n\nThus, the maximum length in meters of #9 is:\n\n**3**"
